19:04.430 --> 19:06.620
with no regard
for the consequences.

19:06.660 --> 19:08.360
They fell in love,
didn't they?

19:08.400 --> 19:10.420
- Yes, they did.
- Good.

19:10.470 --> 19:13.130
I like this kind
of story. Go on.

